         <abstract id="aspace_dc860cdc57baf0954557a4008772a9b3">The records consist of correspondence, member lists, minutes, and ledgers documenting the activities and operations of the Manuscript Society (incorporated as the Wrexham Foundation).</abstract>
         <origination label="creator">
