      <odd id="aspace_19653eead4761b246d8cbb45f0cb852d">
         <head>General note</head>
         <p>Forms part of Yale Record Group 40 (YRG 40), Records of Yale clubs, societies, and organizations.</p>  
      </odd>
      <acqinfo id="aspace_408bd890a043a093956cf17e5f4b87e8">
         <head>Immediate Source of Acquisition</head>
         <p>The records were transferred from the Wrexham Foundation, 2002.</p>  
      </acqinfo>
      <accessrestrict id="aspace_abccc0db70e42a2f27d2a837662da539">
         <head>Conditions Governing Access</head>
         <p>Access to the materials is restricted. Requests for access must be directed to Stephen Parks, or his successor, for approval.</p>
         <p>Some records in this finding aid have been redacted, as they include student names, donor names, and other restricted data. These records will not appear in the published finding aid.</p>  
      </accessrestrict>
      <prefercite id="aspace_cfeac80e1be273cb29a1c63cef69f2bc">
         <head>Preferred Citation</head>
         <p>Wrexham Foundation, Yale University, Records (RU 915). Manuscripts and Archives, Yale University Library.</p>  
      </prefercite>
      <arrangement id="aspace_ac24b9bb703f613199d56126b60e19bd">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>The records are arranged by accession.</p>  
      </arrangement>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_0fdc3bc26ab41fd959a07368a1254922">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The records consist of correspondence, member lists, minutes, and ledgers documenting the activities and operations of the Manuscript Society (incorporated as the Wrexham Foundation).</p>  
      </scopecontent>
